## Running from the CLI

```bash
# Install
pip install nodus-lang

# Run a script
nodus run my_script.nd

# Check syntax
nodus check my_script.nd

# Format
nodus fmt my_script.nd

# With a longer time limit (overrides 200ms default)
nodus run --time-limit 5000 my_script.nd

# Sandbox filesystem access
nodus run --allow-paths /data,/tmp my_script.nd
```
